    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As long as you have a readied action to perform a counter punch, you may abandon your readied action as a free action (even if it is not your turn) and regain martial focus. Abandoning a readied action with this talent does not grant you additional actions.</p>\n<p>In addition, you may forgo selecting an additional trigger in favor of self defense. For each additional trigger you forgo selecting when readying your counter punch, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your armor class until the start of your next turn.</p>\n",
